title: Is Biden Repeating Obama’s Mistakes?
itunes:title: Is Biden Repeating Obama’s Mistakes?
description: The protests in Iran are interfering with President Biden's plan to reenter the nuclear deal with Iran brokered during the Obama Administration. Separately, NATO claims "sabotage" appears to have caused the damage to the Nord Stream pipeline. All signs point to Russia as the culprit. What does this mean for America's foreign policy? Jay, Jordan, and the Sekulow team discuss these topics and more today on Sekulow.
